  "text": "To evaluate the method of calculating the impulse from the digitization data, impulse values were compared in pairs with those obtained by integrating the ground reaction force. The two methods were compared and then statistically substantiated using a Method Validation Tool Kit (http://www.westgard. com/mvtools.html), using a paired data calculator. The resulting value for the observed bias was tested for significance using a Student t-test [CITATION_1] .",
